### ============================================================================
### ERP TEMPLARIOS - SPRINT 5: ASSETS, LIABILITIES, MAINTENANCE, SANCTIONS, DRIVER HISTORY
### Archivo de pruebas para VS Code REST Client
### ============================================================================

### Variables de entorno
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN (Login para obtener token)
### ============================================================================

### Login como admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@templarios.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Guardar token de acceso
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### MÓDULO ASSETS (ACTIVOS DE LA EMPRESA)
### ============================================================================

### Obtener todos los activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener activos con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener activos por categoría
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?category=VEHICLE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener solo activos activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Buscar activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?search=camión
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener categorías de activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas de activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/stats?companyId=COMPANY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener activo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear nuevo activo
# @name createAsset
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "4e9d150c-684b-43ef-9de6-631fad2538d8",
  "name": "Camión Volvo FH 540",
  "description": "Camión tractocarro para transporte internacional",
  "category": "VEHICLE",
  "value": 250000.00,
  "acquisitionDate": "2023-01-15",
  "usefulLifeMonths": 120,
  "depreciation": 50000.00
}

### Actualizar activo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Camión Volvo FH 540 Actualizado",
  "description": "Descripción actualizada",
  "value": 230000.00
}

### Actualizar depreciación
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE/depreciation
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "depreciation": 62500.00
}

### Desactivar activo
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Activar activo
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### CASOS DE ERROR - ASSETS
### ============================================================================

### Error: Crear activo sin nombre (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "COMPANY_ID_HERE",
  "category": "VEHICLE",
  "value": 100000.00
}

### Error: Crear activo con categoría inválida (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "COMPANY_ID_HERE",
  "name": "Activo Test",
  "category": "INVALID_CATEGORY",
  "value": 100000.00
}

### Error: Depreciación mayor al valor (400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/assets/ASSET_ID_HERE/depreciation
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "depreciation": 500000.00
}

### Error: Desactivar activo ya inactivo (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets/INACTIVE_ASSET_ID/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### MÓDULO LIABILITIES (PASIVOS)
### ============================================================================

### Obtener todos los pasivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivos con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivos por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities?type=LOAN
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivos por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivos por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities?companyId=COMPANY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Buscar pasivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities?search=préstamo
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener tipos de pasivo
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/types
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas de pasivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivos vencidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener pasivo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/LIABILITY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear nuevo pasivo
# @name createLiability
POST {{baseUrl}}/liabilities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "COMPANY_ID_HERE",
  "name": "Préstamo Bancario BNB",
  "description": "Préstamo para adquisición de flota",
  "type": "LOAN",
  "amount": 500000.00,
  "interestRate": 8.5,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "dueDate": "2029-01-01"
}

### Actualizar pasivo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/LIABILITY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Préstamo Bancario BNB Actualizado",
  "amount": 480000.00
}

### Actualizar estado de pasivo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/LIABILITY_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "PARTIAL"
}

### Registrar pago parcial
POST {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/LIABILITY_ID_HERE/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 50000.00
}

