### ============================================================================
### MÓDULO MAINTENANCE (MANTENIMIENTOS)
### ============================================================================

### Obtener todos los mantenimientos
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos por camión
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance?truckId=TRUCK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance?type=PREVENTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance?dateFrom=2024-01-01&dateTo=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimientos próximos/pendientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener tipos de mantenimiento
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/types
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas de mantenimiento
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas por camión
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/stats?truckId=TRUCK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial de mantenimientos de un camión
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/truck/TRUCK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener mantenimiento por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/MAINTENANCE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear nuevo mantenimiento
# @name createMaintenance
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "truckId": "e3ea94b5-4a36-4977-9460-f92ac6ff796f",
  "type": "PREVENTIVE",
  "description": "Cambio de aceite y filtros",
  "mileage": 150000,
  "startDate": "2024-06-15",
  "cost": 2500.00,
  "workshop": "Taller Central",
  "notes": "Mantenimiento programado cada 10,000 km"
}

### Actualizar mantenimiento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/MAINTENANCE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Cambio de aceite, filtros y revisión de frenos",
  "cost": 3200.00
}

### Iniciar mantenimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/MAINTENANCE_ID_HERE/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Completar mantenimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/MAINTENANCE_ID_HERE/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "endDate": "2024-06-16",
  "finalCost": 2800.00,
  "notes": "Trabajo completado satisfactoriamente"
}

### Cancelar mantenimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/MAINTENANCE_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "Camión vendido antes del mantenimiento"
}

