### ============================================================================
### MÓDULO SANCTIONS (SANCIONES)
### ============================================================================

### Obtener todas las sanciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones por conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?driverId=DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?type=FINE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?dateFrom=2024-01-01&dateTo=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones activas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener tipos de sanción
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/types
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas de sanciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas por conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/stats?driverId=DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones de un conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/driver/DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanción por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/SANCTION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear nueva sanción
# @name createSanction
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "cad3cb22-ae3a-4418-b9d6-eafe97c57c1b",
  "type": "FINE",
  "reason": "Exceso de velocidad en zona urbana",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "startDate": "2024-06-15",
  "notes": "Infracción detectada por radar"
}

### Crear sanción de suspensión
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "type": "SUSPENSION",
  "reason": "Acumulación de 3 infracciones graves",
  "startDate": "2024-06-15",
  "endDate": "2024-06-30",
  "notes": "Suspensión de 15 días"
}

### Crear amonestación
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "type": "WARNING",
  "reason": "No cumplir con horario de descanso",
  "startDate": "2024-06-15",
  "notes": "Primera amonestación verbal"
}

### Actualizar sanción
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/SANCTION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "Exceso de velocidad en zona escolar",
  "amount": 750.00,
  "notes": "Monto actualizado por gravedad"
}

### Completar sanción
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/SANCTION_ID_HERE/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Cancelar sanción
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/SANCTION_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "Error administrativo - sanción aplicada a conductor incorrecto"
}

