### ============================================================================
### MÓDULO DRIVER HISTORY (HISTORIAL DE CONDUCTORES)
### ============================================================================

### Obtener todo el historial
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial por conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history?driverId=DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial por tipo de evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history?eventType=INCIDENT
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history?dateFrom=2024-01-01&dateTo=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener tipos de evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/event-types
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas del historial
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener estadísticas por conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/stats?driverId=DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener historial de un conductor específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/driver/DRIVER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener timeline de un conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/driver/DRIVER_ID_HERE/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener resumen completo del conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/driver/DRIVER_ID_HERE/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener registro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/HISTORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear registro de historial
# @name createHistory
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "cad3cb22-ae3a-4418-b9d6-eafe97c57c1b",
  "eventType": "INCIDENT",
  "description": "Incidente menor en carretera",
  "notes": "Sin daños materiales ni personales",
  "occurredAt": "2024-06-15T10:30:00Z"
}

### Crear registro de accidente
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "ACCIDENT",
  "description": "Colisión menor en estacionamiento",
  "notes": "Daños menores en parachoques trasero",
  "occurredAt": "2024-06-15"
}

### Crear registro de reconocimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "AWARD",
  "description": "Conductor del mes - Mejor rendimiento",
  "notes": "Reconocimiento por 6 meses sin incidentes",
  "occurredAt": "2024-06-01"
}

### Crear registro de cambio de estado
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "STATUS_CHANGE",
  "description": "Cambio de estado a disponible",
  "notes": "Regreso de licencia médica",
  "occurredAt": "2024-06-15"
}

### Eliminar registro de historial
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/HISTORY_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================================
### CASOS DE ERROR - DRIVER HISTORY
### ============================================================================

### Error: Crear registro sin descripción (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "INCIDENT"
}

### Error: Tipo de evento inválido (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "INVALID_TYPE",
  "description": "Test"
}

### ============================================================================
### FLUJO COMPLETO DE TRABAJO (WORKFLOW)
### ============================================================================

### 1. Login
# @name workflowLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@templarios.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

@workflowToken = {{workflowLogin.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 2. Registrar nuevo activo (vehículo)
# @name workflowAsset
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "COMPANY_ID_HERE",
  "name": "Camión Nuevo Sprinter",
  "description": "Camión para transporte urbano",
  "category": "VEHICLE",
  "value": 180000.00,
  "acquisitionDate": "2024-06-01",
  "usefulLifeMonths": 96
}

@assetId = {{workflowAsset.response.body.data.id}}

### 3. Registrar pasivo (financiamiento)
# @name workflowLiability
POST {{baseUrl}}/liabilities
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "COMPANY_ID_HERE",
  "name": "Financiamiento Camión Sprinter",
  "type": "LOAN",
  "amount": 180000.00,
  "interestRate": 7.5,
  "startDate": "2024-06-01",
  "dueDate": "2027-06-01"
}

@liabilityId = {{workflowLiability.response.body.data.id}}

### 4. Programar mantenimiento preventivo
# @name workflowMaintenance
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "truckId": "TRUCK_ID_HERE",
  "type": "PREVENTIVE",
  "description": "Primer mantenimiento preventivo",
  "mileage": 5000,
  "startDate": "2024-07-01",
  "workshop": "Taller Autorizado"
}

@maintenanceId = {{workflowMaintenance.response.body.data.id}}

### 5. Iniciar mantenimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/{{maintenanceId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}

### 6. Completar mantenimiento
POST {{baseUrl}}/maintenance/{{maintenanceId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "endDate": "2024-07-02",
  "finalCost": 1500.00,
  "notes": "Todo en orden"
}

### 7. Registrar incidente del conductor
# @name workflowHistory
POST {{baseUrl}}/driver-history
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "eventType": "INCIDENT",
  "description": "Llegada tarde por conditions climáticas"
}

@historyId = {{workflowHistory.response.body.data.id}}

### 8. Aplicar sanción
# @name workflowSanction
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "type": "WARNING",
  "reason": "Incumplimiento de horario",
  "startDate": "2024-06-15"
}

@sanctionId = {{workflowSanction.response.body.data.id}}

### 9. Completar sanción
POST {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/{{sanctionId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}

### 10. Actualizar depreciación del activo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/assets/{{assetId}}/depreciation
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "depreciation": 1875.00
}

### 11. Registrar pago del pasivo
POST {{baseUrl}}/liabilities/{{liabilityId}}/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 5000.00
}

### 12. Ver resumen del conductor
GET {{baseUrl}}/driver-history/driver/DRIVER_ID_HERE/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{workflowToken}}

### ============================================================================
### RESUMEN DE ENDPOINTS - SPRINT 5
### ============================================================================
###
### ASSETS (Activos):
### - GET    /assets                    - Listar activos
### - GET    /assets/categories         - Categorías
### - GET    /assets/stats              - Estadísticas
### - GET    /assets/:id                - Detalle de activo
### - POST   /assets                    - Crear activo
### - PUT    /assets/:id                - Actualizar activo
### - PATCH  /assets/:id/depreciation   - Actualizar depreciación
### - POST   /assets/:id/deactivate     - Desactivar activo
### - POST   /assets/:id/activate       - Activar activo
###
### LIABILITIES (Pasivos):
### - GET    /liabilities               - Listar pasivos
### - GET    /liabilities/types         - Tipos de pasivo
### - GET    /liabilities/stats         - Estadísticas
### - GET    /liabilities/overdue       - Pasivos vencidos
### - GET    /liabilities/:id           - Detalle de pasivo
### - POST   /liabilities               - Crear pasivo
### - PUT    /liabilities/:id           - Actualizar pasivo
### - PATCH  /liabilities/:id/status    - Cambiar estado
### - POST   /liabilities/:id/payment   - Registrar pago
###
### MAINTENANCE (Mantenimientos):
### - GET    /maintenance               - Listar mantenimientos
### - GET    /maintenance/upcoming      - Mantenimientos próximos
### - GET    /maintenance/types         - Tipos de mantenimiento
### - GET    /maintenance/stats         - Estadísticas
### - GET    /maintenance/truck/:truckId - Por camión
### - GET    /maintenance/:id           - Detalle
### - POST   /maintenance               - Crear mantenimiento
### - PUT    /maintenance/:id           - Actualizar
### - POST   /maintenance/:id/start     - Iniciar
### - POST   /maintenance/:id/complete  - Completar
### - POST   /maintenance/:id/cancel    - Cancelar
###
### SANCTIONS (Sanciones):
### - GET    /sanctions                 - Listar sanciones
### - GET    /sanctions/active          - Sanciones activas
### - GET    /sanctions/types           - Tipos de sanción
### - GET    /sanctions/stats           - Estadísticas
### - GET    /sanctions/driver/:driverId - Por conductor
### - GET    /sanctions/:id             - Detalle
### - POST   /sanctions                 - Crear sanción
### - PUT    /sanctions/:id             - Actualizar
### - POST   /sanctions/:id/complete    - Completar
### - POST   /sanctions/:id/cancel      - Cancelar
###
### DRIVER HISTORY (Historial):
### - GET    /driver-history            - Listar historial
### - GET    /driver-history/event-types - Tipos de evento
### - GET    /driver-history/stats      - Estadísticas
### - GET    /driver-history/driver/:driverId - Por conductor
### - GET    /driver-history/driver/:driverId/timeline - Timeline
### - GET    /driver-history/driver/:driverId/summary - Resumen
### - GET    /driver-history/:id        - Detalle
### - POST   /driver-history            - Crear registro
### - DELETE /driver-history/:id        - Eliminar
###
